item.title: [HIVE-21711] Regression caused by HIVE-21279 for blobstorage fs
item.description: HIVE-21279 caused a regression wherein CTAS/create materialized views statement for blobstorage is now always renaming files.
item.summary: Regression caused by HIVE-21279 for blobstorage fs

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
